rComments: Very accessible after classes. He is a considerate professor who helps me solve my homework questions. Would recommend my friends to take his class.

Very nice prof and knowledgable in the course material. His class was very organized and always stayed late to answer students questions and also in his office hours. I would have wanted him to explain the processes and theories more in depth, rather than just jumping into examples.
He is ok, it was just a little bit boring

Professor Parimbelli is a great guy. Really fair and caring prof. Goes through examples thoroughly and answers all questions. Always available to see you in office hours. Knows his stuff and will give good feedback on exams. Book is optional, not mandatory but is helpful with some concepts. As long as you go through slides, examples you'll be good.
